column1: # Title: Offshore Wind Average Annual Capacity Factor by ReEDS Wind Region and Class

# Comments: Annual average capacity factor for each ReEDS wind resource region / wind class.  Calculated by taking the average of (8760) hourly net capacity factor profiles for each wind resource region / wind class.
# Source: Information based on ReEDS version 2017.  Files provided by ReEDS team in April 2017.
